Maintainr - A lazy developer utility
===============================================================================

Maintainr is an utility designed to easily maintain small projects and spread
news about them.
Permits to collect todos, update people about progresses via social networks
such as identi.ca and gtk-apps.org, and share spare time among them accordly
a not-so-randomic heuristic.

Maintainr homepage is available at: http://maintainr.barberaware.org/

REQUIREMENTS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Maintainr depends on:

  - libgtk2 >= 2.18.9
  - libxml-2.0 >= 2.7.7
  - twitter-glib >= 0.9.8
  - libgrss >= 0.4
  - libopengdesktop >= 0.4

INSTALLATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
./configure
make
sudo make install

